* remove hugs98-graphics

* remove ghc-6.4.1 (leaving 6.4.1-r1)

* remove hugs98-2005.3 (leaving 2005.3-r1)

== High priority ==

* fix opengl issue with ghc and hugs

* fix modular X dep issue with ghc and hugs

* mark ghc-6.4.1 and ghc-bin-6.4.1 stable on all supported arches
  then prune old versions of ghc (eg 6.4)

== Ebuild maintainance ==

* add gtk2 use flag for wxhaskell, see bug #106560

* get a recent version of gtk2hs fixed and marked stable on sparc and remove
  the really old versions of gtk2hs

* get other ebuilds marked stable on as many arches as we can test:
  alex-2.0.1-r1, c2hs-0.14.5, cabal-1.1.3, drift-2.1.2, gtk2hs-0.9.10,
  haddock-0.7, happy-1.15, hugs98-2005.3-r1, buddha-1.2.

* get ebuilds marked ~amd64: helium, darcs, frown, harp, haskell-src-exts,
